"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-06-22-Olympics-Brazilian-surfers-eye-gold-in-Paris-1uDKMIE6Xv2-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Brazilian surfers who qualified to compete in the Paris Olympics participated in a news conference in Rio de Janeiro on Thursday, organized by the World Surf League (WSL).\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 329, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9999999992046469, \"rank\": 7.954622495683602e-10, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 374, \"end\": 397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Surf League (WSL)\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the event, the athletes expressed their excitement and desire to win in France.\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 478, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8273156131427766, \"rank\": 0.2058960725131007, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's the Olympic gold!\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the biggest sports event in the world, and that is on top of everything.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 596, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's part of our professional careers as surfers.\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am here, I have sponsors, commitments inside and out of the water, all of my team, my family and my friends.\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a huge dream that all athletes have.\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I will win gold,\\\" said Brazilian Olympic surfing qualifier Joan Chianca.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"International Surfing Association's tweet on June 18 about Brazilian surfers who have qualified for the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 882, \"end\": 915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Surfing Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/@ISFsurfing  \\\"I have been preparing for the Olympics since November last year.\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did my pre-season with my team in the Olympic Brazilian Committee,\\\" added fellow Brazilian Olympic surfing qualifier Tatiana Weston-Webb.\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1201, \"end\": 1220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tatiana_Weston-Webb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tatiana Weston-Webb\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tatiana_Weston-Webb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tatiana_Weston-Webb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"During that time, I was training, focused in the Olympic results.\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It only happens every four years, and it's a great opportunity.\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to win in every step I compete in, but my focus is 100 percent the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Surfers from across the globe will convene in Rio de Janeiro between June 22 and 30 to participate in the Rio Pro competition as part of the WSL tour.\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1485, \"end\": 1499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9999999992046469, \"rank\": 7.954622495683602e-10, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 1580, \"end\": 1583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2292579560967642e-33, \"text\": \"WSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The surfing events during the Paris Olympics will take place over four days within a 10-day window, from July 27 to August 5.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(Cover: Brazil's Gabriel Medina rides a wave during the first round of the men's surfing competition at the Summer Olympic Games at Tsurigasaki beach in Ichinomiya, Japan, July 25, 2021.\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1726, \"end\": 1732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.7883357223822767, \"rank\": 0.21256797141705813, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"db